  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>From crystal-clear waters and white sandy beaches to alpine forests and Bronze Age settlements, Sardinia has it all. Join this fascinating escorted tour through the sunning landscapes, along Caribbean-like coastlines and across the glistening sea, spending a week discovering the secrets of Sardinia. This tour has the perfect balance of relaxation in some of the most stunning locations you could imagine, whilst also delving into the island's unique history with with its Greek, Spanish, North African and Italian influences.</span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>26</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/secrets-of-sardinia#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/secrets-of-sardinia#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/secrets-of-sardinia#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/secrets-of-sardinia#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/secrets-of-sardinia#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
